SUMMARY:Afterschool Kids Club-Fall2025
DESCRIPTION:A “Walking School bus” picks up children ages 6-12 years old afterschool from Charles G. Fraser & Ryerson CS to go back to Scadding Court for a variety of daily programs: including reading and bookmaking\, Computer Club\, Arts & crafts\, physical activities\, homework help and more. Activities vary from season to season. A healthy snack is provided. \n\n\n\n2025 Afterschool Kids Club Sessions: Day and Time: Monday to Friday: 3 – 6 pm Fall 2025 session: September 15 – December 12 Place: Scadding Court Community Centre\, Room # 1 $520 for 13 weeks
URL:https://scaddingcourt.org/event/afterschool-kids-club-fall2025/2026-03-16/
LOCATION:Scadding Court Community Centre\, 707 Dundas Street West\, Toronto\, Ontario\, M5T2W6\, Canada
CATEGORIES:Children's Programs
