SUMMARY:Women's Boxing - Winter 2026
DESCRIPTION:Winter 2026 Session: Jan 12th to March 16th.\nDay & Time: Monday 5 pm to 6 pm\nDesigned for youth ages 13–29 who want to build strength\, confidence\, and resilience. Participants will learn boxing fundamentals\, improve fitness\, and develop discipline in a supportive and positive environment.\nContact: Labib at 647-370-1171\, labib@scaddingcourt.org
