SUMMARY:Drop-in Badminton - Boys & Girls: Winter 2026
DESCRIPTION:Winter 2026 Session: Jan 12th to March 16th.\nDay & Time: Monday 6 pm to 8 pm.\n\n \n\nThis fun and active program is available to youth ages 13–17 to learn and play badminton in a friendly and welcoming environment. Players can improve coordination\, teamwork\, and focus through drills and casual matches while staying fit and engaged. All levels are welcome.\nContact: Labib at 647-370-1171\, labib@scaddingcourt.org
URL:https://scaddingcourt.org/event/drop-in-badminton-boys-girls-winter-2026/2026-03-16/
