SUMMARY:TUFF - Mind in Motion - Winter 2026
DESCRIPTION:Session: Winter 2026 Date: Jan 14th to March 18th Time: Wednesdays 6:00 pm to 9:00 pm \n\n\n\nIt’s a free youth program designed to help you build confidence \, connect with others\, and strengthen your overall well-being. Through fun\, peer-led workshops\, shared meals\, and creative activities\, we focus on: – Boosting self-esteem and resilience – Building healthy coping skills – Making new friends and connections – Moving your body + engaging your mind
