DESCRIPTION:Children’s Ready to Rebound Basketball Program \n\n\n\nFREE – Funded by MLSE What: Learn basketball with a qualified instructor. Drills\, techniques\, skill building and more. Please wear appropriate shoes for the gym. When: Every Thursday Children 6 – 9 years old: 4 pm – 5 pm Children 10- 12 years old: 5 pm – 6 pm Session: Fall 2025: September 18 – December 4 Place: Scadding Court Community Centre Gym Registration: On the Portal – https://scccportal.org/ \n\n\n\nFor more information: Vivian Vivian@scaddingcourt.org OR Labib labib@scaddingcourt.org
