SUMMARY:FoodFit for Mandarin Speaking Newcomers: Winter 2026
DESCRIPTION:A 12 week cooking program for people of all ability levels. Focused on building our nutritional literacy and promoting healthy habits\, this program helps balance diets with tasty\, affordable recipes. We increase our physical activity levels by focusing on daily walking as a form of easy and cost-free exercise.\n\n\n\nSession: Winter 2026\, Jan 9 – April 3\nDay and time: Fridays\, 11 am – 2:00 pm\nLocation: Scadding Court downstairs kitchen\n\n \n\nFor more information\, contact katie@scaddingcourt.org
URL:https://scaddingcourt.org/event/foodfit-for-mandarin-speaking-newcomers-winter-2026/2026-03-20/
